data.description: Price decreased. !  Stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bath home in prime location! This spacious gem boasts a perfect layout for modern living. Retreat to the luxurious master suite with its own en-suite bath.  Close to Downtown Kissimmee and 15 minutes from the Theme Parks. Your dream home awaits – don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Contact us today to schedule a viewing.  the 4 beddroom is located on the second floor as a bonus room , which includes a private bathroom, closet, and a door.
